snippet.title: Abyssus Deep Under - Trailer 2024
snippet.description:
Here's the trailer for our game, Abyssus Deep Under! Dive into an aquatic world full of secrets, manage your own army, devise strategies, and become the new master of the Abyss!

A worthy heir to the golden age of strategy games with a modern twist, blending the best of gameplay elements: RTS, 4X, and MMO.

Join our community of passionate gamers and keep up to date with the latest news about Abyssus Deep Under!

⬇️ You can follow us here! ⬇️
🌐 https://www.abyssus-deep-under.com/ 🌐
📸 https://www.instagram.com/abyssus.deep.under/ 📸
❌ https://www.twitter.com/ADU_Ouebsson ❌
📱https://www.tiktok.com/@abyssus.deep.under 📱

Abyssus Deep Under is a MMORTS/4X game in which you play as an Octaly on a mission to explore the world of Abyssus. And if you dare... you can even venture into its heart: the Abyss, a dungeon as deep as it is mysterious...

Subscribe to not miss a single video! 😉

-------
Song: Aliaksei Yukhnevich - End of the Abyss (No Copyright Music)
Music provided by Tunetank.
Free Download:  https://bit.ly/2xtEXR1
Video Link:   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hoap3gfnrgo
-------
